{"tid":965412,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今夏自由球員豪華陣：洛賓列貝利保方法比藍斯   大牌雲集","createTime":"2019-01-02T04:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T03:20:18.000Z","uid":4661,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"215e477b05eae9e3e0f8efa293328775709821d5","tid":965412,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T04:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/01/02/6/69b4741cf4740e8c090724418cef96e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F01%2F02%2F6%2F69b4741cf4740e8c090724418cef96e2.jpg&h=c6d31001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n進入2019年之後，很多大牌球星的合同只剩下半年時間，他們現在能夠跟任何球隊進行談判。考慮到轉會市場的水漲船高，免費簽約這些大牌球星無疑是一種不錯的選擇。<br />\n　　西班牙媒體《馬卡報》羅列了一份今夏將成為自由球員的名單。<br />\n　　門將位置，40歲的保方將成為自由球員，此外36歲的阿仙奴門將施治也將成為自由球員，他們的合約都只剩下半年。<br />\n　　後防線上，35歲的艾維斯跟巴黎只剩下半年合約。32歲的高甸、33歲的菲臘比-路斯、33歲的祖安科蘭，他們與馬體會的合約只剩下半年。31歲的大衛-路斯與車路士的合約，也只剩下半年。<br />\n　　中場方面，23歲的拉比奧成為轉會市場的熱門，他已經決定不跟巴黎續約，目前跟巴塞走得很接近。31歲的法比加斯、29歲的靴里拉、34歲的卡蘇拿、27歲的藍斯、30歲的馬達，他們的合約都只剩下半年。<br />\n　　鋒線方面，拜仁「羅貝里」組合都進入了合約年，34歲的洛賓、35歲的列貝利，他們的合約都只剩下半年。32歲的基奧特與車路士也只有半年合約。<br />\n<br />\n另外，37歲的阿度里斯跟畢爾包也只有半年合約，而33歲的洛蘭迪跟熱刺只剩下半年合約。<br />\n　　今夏合約到期球員最佳十一人：保方；艾維斯、高甸、大衛-路斯、菲臘比-路斯；拉比奧、法比加斯、靴里拉；洛賓、基奧特、列貝利。<br />\n　　候選：施治、祖安科蘭、卡蘇拿、藍斯、馬達、史杜列治、巴洛迪利、阿度里斯、洛蘭迪。"},{"pid":"4c943e50d753d37789236697e63ebaba151ad6bd","tid":965412,"uid":38841,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:01:26.000Z","msg":"前鋒勁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afacb14d48e9ef0ceaf27ce617d235e9be954be4","tid":965412,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c943e50d753d37789236697e63ebaba151ad6bd","tid":965412,"uid":38841,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:01:26.000Z","msg":"前鋒勁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a2b17ad01ff6d66e423f798543567e65ac5374","tid":965412,"uid":95,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4c943e50d753d37789236697e63ebaba151ad6bd","tid":965412,"uid":38841,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:01:26.000Z","msg":"前鋒勁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:08:13.000Z","msg":"豬腦仲咁有型<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，另外兩件成個呀叔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866a81c4eb9c93313de898722bac0636c9b11597","tid":965412,"uid":59920,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.kitchee.com/images/master/kitchee_logo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kitchee.com%2Fimages%2Fmaster%2Fkitchee_logo.png&h=5aaebab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243a3d37bde1af894eb2f54310874736fb48aa8e","tid":965412,"uid":62891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:38:33.000Z","msg":"個陣占士米拿都冇已經唔駛睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2599ffad50af1b33e29e0d4287608caf6ecbfb94","tid":965412,"uid":130060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:59:14.000Z","msg":"認真車仔簽阿度列斯番黎 都可能勁過摩拉達<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ced0b143b1eb0badf8c48529d849d394aa994d","ti